Squizzy::
She slowly came out of the stasis lock, but was still alseep.  Her 
head moved slightly and then she layed perfectly still.

Feline::
She saw the bot on the table move and took a few steps towards the 
vile that Zardus had left for her to use.  She looked back and saw 
that the bot wasn't awake. She waited to see it the bot would wake 
up. Her ears perked up as she heard Zardus' voice and another's 
coming closer to the lab.  She looked at the doorway and then back at 
the bot on the table.
